16:02.562 --> 16:05.196
He's -- he's gay --
-what?

16:05.198 --> 16:06.297
I mean,
long story, but --

16:06.299 --> 16:09.534
well, tell me.

16:09.536 --> 16:11.302
[ Sighs ]

16:11.304 --> 16:12.804
Well, one time I went
over to his apartment

16:12.806 --> 16:13.938
to check on my sister.

16:13.940 --> 16:16.374
And, uh -- and he just
came outside and kissed me

16:16.376 --> 16:18.776
and I hit him.

16:18.778 --> 16:21.012
I hope you hit him hard.

16:21.014 --> 16:22.914
-Well, damn, Veronica.
-What?

16:22.916 --> 16:25.450
I mean, that is your son, still.
It's kind of harsh.

16:25.452 --> 16:26.651
Yeah,
but he had no business

16:26.653 --> 16:28.686
trying to kiss
another man.

16:30.390 --> 16:36.160
Especially a man
his mother enjoys kissing.

16:36.162 --> 16:39.731
Well, look,
that was way before...

16:39.733 --> 16:41.432
Me and you.

16:41.434 --> 16:46.904
