16:46.906 --> 16:49.574
you ever think about it?

16:49.576 --> 16:53.644
��

16:53.646 --> 16:56.214
I'm gonna go
get your things.

16:56.216 --> 16:58.649
Yeah,
you think about it.

16:58.651 --> 16:59.917
[ Both laugh ]

16:59.919 --> 17:02.987
Probably as much
as I do.

17:02.989 --> 17:05.656
I got to go.

17:05.657 --> 17:07.458
Purse?

17:09.061 --> 17:11.429
[ Purse unzips ]
[ Coughs ]

17:11.431 --> 17:13.464
[ Keys jingle ]

17:13.465 --> 17:17.935
��

17:17.936 --> 17:19.270
-hurry back.
-See you. Yeah.

17:19.271 --> 17:20.771
Hurry back. Okay?

17:20.773 --> 17:23.840
Okay. Feel better.

17:23.843 --> 17:32.383
��

17:32.385 --> 17:35.420
[ indistinct P.A. Announcement ]

17:35.422 --> 17:37.088
-So?
-What?

17:37.090 --> 17:38.689
What happened?

17:38.691 --> 17:39.624
Nothing.

17:39.626 --> 17:41.092
She ain't write you
a check?

17:41.094 --> 17:43.294
-What are you talking about?
-Well, you saved that old girl.

17:43.296 --> 17:45.096
She should be
writing you a check.

17:45.098 --> 17:48.566
No, no. She just wanted me to
get some things from her place.

17:48.568 --> 17:49.767
Why?

17:49.769 --> 17:51.402
I guess she's staying here
for another night.

17:51.404 --> 17:52.970
Ah.

17:52.972 --> 17:55.840
So,
you're the errand boy now.

17:55.842 --> 17:56.974
-No, I'm not.
-Yeah.

17:56.976 --> 18:00.778
Hey, you got to make
sure she's happy. I get it.

18:00.780 --> 18:02.914
Yeah, come on.

18:02.916 --> 18:04.882
Oh, what?
I'm -- I'm taking you?

18:04.884 --> 18:06.284
Yeah, you know I don't
got a car. Come on.

18:06.286 --> 18:07.518
Oh, so,
I'm the cabbie now?

18:07.520 --> 18:08.719
Dude, just come on.

18:08.721 --> 18:10.021
-All right.
-All right, cool.

18:10.023 --> 18:11.489
When's your uncle
getting back?

18:11.491 --> 18:12.590
Uh, I don't know.
Maybe I'll hit him up.

18:12.592 --> 18:13.357
-Yeah.
-Yeah?

18:13.359 --> 18:15.860
Yeah, hit him
up. Come on.

18:15.862 --> 18:18.996
Yo?

18:18.998 --> 18:23.234
You play this right,
you won't even need my uncle.

18:23.236 --> 18:26.571
-What are you saying?
-That chick's got money, man.

18:26.573 --> 18:29.440
I'm telling you,
she'll buy that truck for you.

18:29.442 --> 18:30.074
Yeah. Whatever.

18:30.076 --> 18:31.476
Oh, come on, man.

18:31.478 --> 18:33.044
What, you've been hitting that.
You could work that out.

18:33.046 --> 18:34.011
Dude, will you shut up?

18:34.013 --> 18:35.913
Yo, I'm telling you,

18:35.915 --> 18:39.250
I saw the way she looked
at you when you saved her.

18:39.252 --> 18:40.751
That chick's
in love with you, bro.

18:40.753 --> 18:42.787
-Will you cut it out?
-No.

18:42.789 --> 18:45.156
All's I'm saying,
is you should hit her up

18:45.158 --> 18:48.259
for that truck
instead of my uncle.

18:48.261 --> 18:50.595
Let me tell you something
about this girl.

18:50.597 --> 18:52.997
She's more dangerous
than your uncle is.

18:52.999 --> 18:55.933
[ Scoffs ] Yeah, yeah, yeah.
How the hell you figure that?

18:55.935 --> 18:57.935
-I just got a feeling, man.
-Yeah. All right.

18:57.937 --> 19:00.404
-Can we go?
-Come on.

19:08.298 --> 19:10.064
Wow.

19:10.066 --> 19:11.432
What?

19:11.434 --> 19:13.935
That was a great speech.

19:13.937 --> 19:15.069
Landon...

19:15.071 --> 19:17.505
I mean, you just keep
getting better and better.

19:21.244 --> 19:24.011
You're always
my cheerleader.

19:24.013 --> 19:27.348
Well,
you are very special, sir.

19:27.350 --> 19:30.351
Yeah. Well, thank you.

19:33.189 --> 19:36.057
I've cleared your morning.

19:36.059 --> 19:39.260
Oh, great.
I get a morning?

19:39.262 --> 19:42.296
And you can have
a long night.

19:42.298 --> 19:44.332
Yeah, right.

19:44.334 --> 19:46.133
You can.

19:47.770 --> 19:49.804
With who?

19:49.806 --> 19:51.339
I know someone.

19:51.341 --> 19:53.574
Is she beautiful?

19:53.576 --> 19:55.409
I was talking about me.

19:55.411 --> 19:57.378
[ Laughs ]

19:57.380 --> 19:58.679
Landon...

19:58.681 --> 20:02.516
No, sir, we've stayed up late
and gotten drunk before.

20:02.518 --> 20:04.719
Yeah, I know, but...

20:04.721 --> 20:06.087
Tonight, I'm exhausted.

20:06.089 --> 20:10.458
I just... I just want
to go to bed.

20:10.460 --> 20:11.993
Then so be it.

20:11.995 --> 20:13.928
Cool.

20:17.133 --> 20:19.000
[ Sighs ]

20:20.737 --> 20:22.603
Have you checked on her?

20:22.605 --> 20:23.971
Yes, sir.

20:23.973 --> 20:25.873
I may want you
to pay her a visit soon.

20:28.144 --> 20:31.379
Is that right?

20:31.381 --> 20:33.347
Yeah.

20:33.349 --> 20:36.183
Well then, who will be here
to take care of you, sir?

20:36.185 --> 20:41.289
Landon, I'm a grown man.
I can take care of myself.

20:41.291 --> 20:43.691
Yes, sir, I know you can.

20:43.693 --> 20:45.893
Okay. So...

20:45.895 --> 20:48.029
Could you do that?

20:48.031 --> 20:49.563
Yes, I can.

20:49.565 --> 20:52.133
Um...

20:52.135 --> 20:54.669
After the interviews
that we've set up,

20:54.671 --> 20:57.171
I will get on a plane.

20:57.173 --> 21:00.141
Oh, and, um...
Keep me updated.

21:00.143 --> 21:02.877
Yes, sir, I will.

21:02.879 --> 21:05.112
Let me see the schedule
for tomorrow.

21:05.114 --> 21:08.049
Oh, yes.
Got it right here.

21:09.585 --> 21:11.986
[ Birds chirping ]

21:18.661 --> 21:21.395
-Gia?
-Hi.

21:21.397 --> 21:23.030
Here.

21:23.032 --> 21:24.265
Okay.

21:24.267 --> 21:26.801
And I just bought this.

21:26.803 --> 21:28.202
Thank you.

21:28.204 --> 21:30.104
And make sure
you tell Candace

21:30.106 --> 21:31.973
that I brought them
as soon as you called.

21:31.975 --> 21:35.843
You got me?
-Yeah. Is she your pimp?

21:35.845 --> 21:37.912
[ Chuckles ]
No, she's not.

21:37.914 --> 21:42.083
Well then, why did you run and
grab this stuff so fast for her?

21:42.085 --> 21:42.850
Just tell her what I said.

21:42.852 --> 21:46.487
I have to get out of here.

21:46.489 --> 21:48.656
Not so fast.

21:48.658 --> 21:51.492
Oh. Hey, Candace.

21:51.494 --> 21:53.427
Say "hey" to me
one more time

21:53.429 --> 21:57.765
and I will get a bottle
and smash it across your face.

21:57.767 --> 22:00.001
Please, don't.

22:00.003 --> 22:01.469
You working on my money?

22:01.471 --> 22:04.071
Yes, and I brought the clothes
that you asked for.

22:04.073 --> 22:05.172
She has them.

22:05.174 --> 22:07.942
Better be some nice stuff.

22:07.944 --> 22:10.478
It is.
All designer labels.

22:10.480 --> 22:11.345
How does it feel, Erica?

22:11.347 --> 22:13.481
How -- how does what feel?

22:13.483 --> 22:16.851
To be out here exposed
with nobody watching your back?

22:20.056 --> 22:22.490
Not good.

22:22.492 --> 22:25.159
That's what happens
when you cross me.

22:25.161 --> 22:26.460
I'm sorry.

22:26.462 --> 22:29.096
Do you want me
to slap you?

22:29.098 --> 22:30.364
No.

22:30.366 --> 22:34.135
Then don't say sorry,
when you knew damn-well

22:34.137 --> 22:37.371
what was going down
when you were with war.

22:37.373 --> 22:41.208
You're right, I did.
I knew.

22:41.210 --> 22:42.309
You'd better be
working on David

22:42.311 --> 22:43.978
and you'd better
be working fast.

22:43.980 --> 22:46.013
Okay.

22:46.015 --> 22:47.081
100k.

22:47.083 --> 22:48.516
[ Scoffs ] Okay.

22:48.518 --> 22:50.418
I mean, I don't know
how I'm going to get that.

22:50.420 --> 22:52.520
You'd better.

22:52.522 --> 22:53.220
But I will figure it out.

22:53.222 --> 22:56.057
Get your ass out of here.

22:56.059 --> 23:01.796
��

23:01.798 --> 23:04.732
[ sighs ]

23:04.734 --> 23:07.868
You need to get dressed.
I need to put you to work.

23:07.870 --> 23:09.603
-Okay.
-Do you have a room?

23:09.605 --> 23:11.005
No.

23:11.007 --> 23:12.673
You can use mine.

23:12.675 --> 23:14.008
But walk ahead of me.

23:14.010 --> 23:18.279
This is the last time
we'll be talking in public.

23:18.281 --> 23:21.649
-Okay.
-You don't know me in public.

23:21.651 --> 23:23.918
Okay.

23:23.920 --> 23:25.820
I'll meet you up there.

23:28.658 --> 23:31.092
[ Sighs ]

23:33.262 --> 23:35.529
-Ma'am?
-Yes?

23:35.531 --> 23:37.164
You're under arrest.

23:37.166 --> 23:39.266
For?

23:39.268 --> 23:40.434
Let's not do this
loud in here.

23:40.436 --> 23:42.369
Let's keep it quiet.
-I beg your pardon?

23:42.371 --> 23:45.172
-You're under arrest.
-For?

23:45.174 --> 23:49.009
You will not cause a scene here,
please.

23:49.011 --> 23:50.478
Yeah,
but can I see some I.D.?

23:50.480 --> 23:53.647
You see this lady?
She's with the police. I'm vice.

23:53.649 --> 23:55.616
Please,
go to the car with her.

23:56.886 --> 23:58.319
What am I being
arrested for?

23:58.321 --> 23:59.320
Robbery.

23:59.322 --> 24:00.588
I don't know
anything about that.

24:00.590 --> 24:02.723
Well, we have a gentleman
who says that you robbed him.

24:02.725 --> 24:05.459
So, please come to the car.
-I didn't do a thing.

24:05.461 --> 24:06.560
Ma'am,
this is a nice place.

24:06.562 --> 24:10.197
You don't want
to cause a scene.

24:10.199 --> 24:12.700
Okay. Okay.

24:12.702 --> 24:14.201
Walk to the door.

24:14.203 --> 24:16.904
We'll do the handcuffs
outside.

24:16.906 --> 24:19.073
[ Birds chirping ]

24:20.576 --> 24:22.476
-Hey.
-Hey.

24:22.478 --> 24:25.079
How are you?

24:25.081 --> 24:26.580
I'm okay.

24:26.582 --> 24:28.983
-You sure?
-Mm-hmm.

24:28.985 --> 24:31.919
-Okay.
-What's going on?

24:31.921 --> 24:34.989
Nothing.

24:34.991 --> 24:36.457
Sure you're okay?

24:36.459 --> 24:38.092
Yeah.

24:40.363 --> 24:43.364
-Okay.
-What's going on?

24:43.366 --> 24:44.899
Well...

24:44.901 --> 24:48.135
Derek said you didn't sound
too happy on the phone.

24:48.137 --> 24:50.738
Well, you know
what I've been going through.

24:50.740 --> 24:53.340
Yeah.

24:53.342 --> 24:57.111
But he offered
to take you out.

24:57.113 --> 24:58.612
Wait.

24:58.614 --> 25:00.915
What?

25:00.917 --> 25:03.517
-Are you doing this?
-Doing what?

25:03.519 --> 25:06.287
You trying to get that man
to ask me out?

25:06.289 --> 25:08.689
[ Laughing ]
No. I promise.

25:08.691 --> 25:10.291
Yes, you are.

25:10.293 --> 25:12.993
No.
He wanted to on his own.

25:12.995 --> 25:15.329
Okay, so that's why
he did my dishes?

25:15.331 --> 25:17.264
-Did he?
-Yes.

25:17.266 --> 25:19.500
Well, I didn't tell him
to do that.

25:19.502 --> 25:21.268
Yeah, right.

25:21.270 --> 25:23.270
No, I didn't.

25:23.272 --> 25:26.407
But you did tell him
to ask me out?

25:26.409 --> 25:28.008
No.

25:29.478 --> 25:31.912
[ Sighs ] Well...

25:31.914 --> 25:35.583
I thought
it would be nice.

25:35.585 --> 25:36.350
I'm not in the mood.

25:36.352 --> 25:39.320
Hanna, just...

25:39.322 --> 25:41.288
Don't you just want
to go out for coffee?

25:41.290 --> 25:42.890
No, I mean...

25:42.892 --> 25:44.858
You know what
I've been dealing with.

25:44.860 --> 25:47.895
All the more reason
for you to get out.

25:47.897 --> 25:51.232
[ Sighs ]

25:51.234 --> 25:53.033
I'm not.

25:53.035 --> 25:55.836
Yes, you are.

25:55.838 --> 25:57.504
Look...

25:59.041 --> 26:00.908
He's just asking
you out for coffee.

26:00.910 --> 26:04.945
Don't you want to get out
and smile some?

26:04.947 --> 26:08.015
I mean, I know it's been
awhile since I laughed -- yes.

26:08.017 --> 26:09.450
Then go with him.

26:09.452 --> 26:11.352
Oh.

26:12.722 --> 26:14.755
Who is this man?

26:14.757 --> 26:16.523
Derek? [ Chuckles ]

26:16.525 --> 26:18.158
He's been working
with our properties

26:18.160 --> 26:19.293
and projects for years now.

26:19.295 --> 26:20.594
You know,
i don't know why

26:20.596 --> 26:22.529
I didn't think about
him for you sooner.

26:22.531 --> 26:24.932
'Cause there probably
was a reason.

26:24.934 --> 26:27.234
-Well, his wife, she --
-yeah, that would do it.

26:27.236 --> 26:30.471
She died a year ago

26:30.473 --> 26:32.840
and he's been lonely,
too.

26:32.842 --> 26:35.676
You should go.

26:35.678 --> 26:37.678
I hear you.

26:39.782 --> 26:42.249
I'm not gonna take no
for an answer.

26:42.251 --> 26:44.551
Well, you don't
really have a choice.

26:46.389 --> 26:47.688
You know what?

26:47.690 --> 26:48.956
I'm going to call him up,

26:48.958 --> 26:50.557
have him pick you up
tomorrow night,

26:50.559 --> 26:53.160
take you out to dinner
or movie or something.

26:53.162 --> 26:55.162
-I thought you said coffee.
-Oh, no, you blew that.

26:55.164 --> 26:56.263
Now,
you're really going out.

26:56.265 --> 26:57.264
Don't.

26:57.266 --> 26:59.133
-Oh, yes, you are.
-No, I'm not.

26:59.135 --> 27:00.234
I'm going to come over here
and push you out the door.

27:00.236 --> 27:01.268
Katheryn, I mean it.

27:01.270 --> 27:03.237
I don't want to hear
another word about it.

27:03.239 --> 27:05.639
-No.
-You're going.

27:05.641 --> 27:08.409
I said, no.

27:08.411 --> 27:09.843
[ Sighs ]

27:09.845 --> 27:12.146
Hanna...

27:14.617 --> 27:16.750
Fine. Fine. Okay.

27:16.752 --> 27:19.753
Okay. Thank you.

27:19.755 --> 27:21.155
Well, are you still
gonna come by later?

27:21.157 --> 27:23.957
-Yeah.
-Okay.

27:23.959 --> 27:26.527
But don't play no games.

27:26.529 --> 27:27.995
Like what?

27:27.997 --> 27:29.063
Don't try to set me up.

27:29.065 --> 27:31.598
I'm not doing that,
okay?

27:31.600 --> 27:35.102
This maid needs help or she's
not gonna be there that long.

27:35.104 --> 27:36.937
Okay.

27:36.939 --> 27:38.105
All right.

27:38.107 --> 27:40.040
-I'll see you later.
-I'll see you later.

27:40.042 --> 27:41.675
Muah.

27:41.677 --> 27:43.477
Take care.
-Yeah.

27:43.479 --> 27:45.746
-Give my love to Benny.
I will.

27:51.370 --> 27:52.336
[ Knock on door ]

27:52.338 --> 27:54.138
Jim:
Come on in! Door's open!

27:54.140 --> 27:56.707
[ Ice clatters ]

27:56.709 --> 28:04.081
��

28:04.083 --> 28:07.117
well, hello.
-Hi.

28:07.119 --> 28:08.786
-Would you like a drink?
-No.

28:08.788 --> 28:10.354
I can't stay long.

28:10.356 --> 28:13.490
-Oh, I beg to differ.
-Jim, please.

28:13.492 --> 28:15.459
You should really
have that drink.

28:15.461 --> 28:17.327
I can't stay.

28:17.329 --> 28:19.563
Suit yourself.

28:19.565 --> 28:22.366
I'll have a double.

28:22.368 --> 28:23.500
So, you wanted to see me?

28:23.502 --> 28:25.602
Yeah.

28:25.604 --> 28:27.738
Wow. You look so...

28:27.740 --> 28:30.407
Formal.
Not at all like I remember.

28:30.409 --> 28:31.675
Well, I've grown up.

28:31.677 --> 28:33.377
-Have you now?
-Yes.

28:33.379 --> 28:35.279
-Really?
-Getting married.

28:35.281 --> 28:36.914
-Is that so?
-Yes.

28:36.916 --> 28:39.016
He's a judge.

28:39.018 --> 28:41.652
A judge?

28:41.654 --> 28:44.088
Do I know this judge?

28:44.090 --> 28:46.957
Kalamit.

28:46.959 --> 28:49.259
Oh, come on?

28:49.261 --> 28:51.495
That old bastard is old enough
to be your grandfather.

28:51.497 --> 28:52.863
Well,
i don't see it that way.

28:52.865 --> 28:54.198
Mmm, you always did
have daddy issues,

28:54.200 --> 28:55.966
even when you
were with me.

28:55.968 --> 28:57.234
That was long ago.

28:57.236 --> 28:59.436
Wasn't that long ago.

28:59.438 --> 29:02.506
So, tell me,
grown-up Sarah...

29:02.508 --> 29:04.241
What did he do for you?

29:04.243 --> 29:05.876
I'm sorry?

29:05.878 --> 29:08.178
Come on, this whole
assistant D.A. Job,

29:08.180 --> 29:10.280
he landed that gig
for you, didn't he?

29:10.282 --> 29:12.049
No.
I worked very hard.

29:12.051 --> 29:13.417
Well,
you worked me very hard.

29:13.419 --> 29:15.285
I'm not
that college girl who --

29:15.287 --> 29:17.754
no, no, no. You're a grown,
adult woman who --

29:17.756 --> 29:19.590
look, Jim, I'm sorry.
I won't do this.

29:19.592 --> 29:20.757
I won't
be intimidated by --

29:20.759 --> 29:22.493
who said anything
about intimidating you?

29:22.495 --> 29:24.027
All the cloak and dagger,

29:24.029 --> 29:25.562
sending your guy
to the D.A.'S office.

29:25.564 --> 29:27.297
Counselor, all I did
was hand somebody a telephone.

29:27.299 --> 29:28.999
Well, I appreciate
you wanting to see me --

29:29.001 --> 29:30.300
sit down and shut up.

29:30.302 --> 29:32.136
No. I'm leaving
and you're gonna be prosecuted.

29:32.138 --> 29:33.537
That's exactly
what I wanted to talk --

29:33.539 --> 29:36.273
-I'm leaving!
-Come on. Would you relax?!

29:36.275 --> 29:38.208
You're gonna sit down
on the corner of that bed

29:38.210 --> 29:41.044
and you're gonna shut up.

29:41.046 --> 29:43.413
Jim.

29:43.415 --> 29:46.650
[ Sighs ]

29:46.652 --> 29:48.018
Young lady,
do you think for a minute,

29:48.020 --> 29:50.621
I'm gonna let the D.A. Bury me,
without first

29:50.623 --> 29:53.257
burying every son-of-a-bitch
